You are a senior frontend developer and UI designer. Build a premium, 
production-ready single-page company website for "Devloom Technologies" 
— a early-stage software startup that builds developer tools, 
AI-powered products, and collaborative platforms.

=== TECH STACK ===
- React + Vite
- Tailwind CSS
- Framer Motion (for all animations)
- React Router (single page, anchor scroll only)
- Google Fonts via @import
- NO backend, NO API calls, NO forms that submit anywhere

=== BRAND IDENTITY ===
Company: Devloom Technologies
Tagline: "Where ideas become infrastructure."
Description: "We build software products for builders — tools that 
eliminate friction, accelerate collaboration, and bring ideas to life faster."
Colors:
  - Primary bg: #080B12 (deep space black, slight blue undertone)
  - Surface: #0D1117
  - Card bg: #111827
  - Accent blue: #3B82F6
  - Accent glow: #2563EB
  - Text primary: #E8EDF5
  - Text secondary: #6B7280
  - Border: #1E2B42

Fonts:
  - Display/heading: "Syne" (Google Fonts) — geometric, futuristic
  - Body: "DM Sans" (Google Fonts) — clean, readable

=== LOGO ===
The company has an SVG logo already. Create a logo component 
(DevloomLogo.jsx) that renders this SVG inline:
- The mark: a geometric loom/grid pattern (intersecting lines forming 
  a tight grid, 4 vertical + 5 horizontal lines) with:
  - 4 corner dots in #3B82F6
  - Intersection nodes (3 key ones) as filled blue circles
  - Hidden </> brackets subtly visible at center in #3B82F6 opacity 0.6
  - Outer frame: 2 corner dots top, 2 bottom in accent blue
- The wordmark: "Dev" in font-weight 600 color #FFFFFF + "loom" in 
  weight 300 color #E8EDF5, font: Syne, size adjustable via props
- "TECHNOLOGIES" below in letter-spacing: 0.28em, size ~35% of main, 
  color #3E4E6A
- Component accepts size prop (sm/md/lg) to scale everything
- Horizontal layout: mark LEFT, wordmark RIGHT

=== SECTIONS (single page, scroll) ===

── 1. NAVBAR ──
- Fixed top, blur backdrop (backdrop-filter: blur(12px)), 
  bg rgba(8,11,18,0.8)
- Left: DevloomLogo size="sm"
- Right: nav links — About, Product, Vision, Contact
  (smooth scroll to sections)
- Nav links: hover → accent blue underline slides in from left
- On scroll >50px: thin bottom border appears (border-color: #1E2B42)
- Mobile: hamburger → slide-down menu

── 2. HERO SECTION ──
Height: 100vh, centered content

Background: 
- Deep #080B12 base
- Subtle dot grid pattern (CSS radial-gradient dots, very faint #1E2B42)
- 3 large blurred circles (position: absolute, blur 120px):
    Circle 1: top-right, #2563EB opacity 0.06, size 500px
    Circle 2: bottom-left, #1E3A5F opacity 0.08, size 400px  
    Circle 3: center, #3B82F6 opacity 0.03, size 600px

Content (staggered Framer Motion entrance, each 0.15s delay apart):
- Small pill badge top: "✦ Software for Builders" — border #1E2B42, 
  bg #0D1117, text #6B7280, tiny dot pulses in blue
- H1 (72px, Syne, weight 700, line-height 1.1):
    Line 1: "We build tools"  
    Line 2: "that builders" (color: #3B82F6)
    Line 3: "rely on."
- Subtext (18px, DM Sans, #6B7280, max-width 480px):
    "Devloom Technologies crafts software products — 
    from collaborative IDEs to AI-powered workflows — 
    built with precision, for the people shaping what comes next."
- Two CTA buttons:
    Primary: "See Our Work" — solid #3B82F6, hover → slightly lighter, 
             subtle scale(1.02) on hover
    Secondary: "Our Vision" — transparent, border #1E2B42, 
               hover → border #3B82F6, text white

Scroll indicator bottom-center: thin vertical line + "scroll" text, 
subtle bounce animation

── 3. ABOUT SECTION ──
id="about", padding 120px vertical

Left col (large, 55%):
- Section label: "WHO WE ARE" in tiny tracked caps, #3B82F6
- H2 (52px Syne): "A small team with an obsession for craft."
- Body text (DM Sans 17px, #9CA3AF, line-height 1.8):
    "Devloom Technologies is an early-stage software company 
    built by developers, for developers. We're not chasing trends — 
    we're solving the problems we've faced ourselves: fragmented tools, 
    broken collaboration, and the friction between an idea and its execution.
    
    We build with precision. We ship with purpose. And we believe the 
    best software quietly becomes the infrastructure others build on top of."

Right col (45%): 
- 3 stat cards stacked, each: border-left 2px #3B82F6, 
  pl-4, bg #111827, rounded-lg, p-5
  Card 1: "01 / Founded" → "2024 — built from a real problem, not a pitch."
  Card 2: "02 / Focus" → "Developer tools, AI workflows, collaborative platforms."
  Card 3: "03 / Philosophy" → "Ship things that last. Build for builders."

Animate: left col slides in from left, right col from right, on scroll 
(use Framer Motion whileInView)

── 4. PRODUCT SECTION ──
id="product", padding 120px vertical, bg #0D1117

Section label: "WHAT WE'RE BUILDING"
H2: "Our flagship product."

Single large product card — full width, max-w-4xl, centered:
bg: #111827, border: #1E2B42, rounded-2xl, p-10
Inside:
  - Top row: product name "CodeSync.ai" (Syne 36px, white) + 
    status badge "In Development" (small pill, amber color)
  - Tagline: "Real-time AI-powered collaborative development." 
    (#9CA3AF, 18px)
  - Divider line #1E2B42
  - 4 feature pills in a flex-wrap row:
    "Monaco Editor" / "Real-time Sync" / "AI Assistant" / "Video Calls"
    Each pill: bg #0D1117, border #1E2B42, text #6B7280, 
    hover → border #3B82F6, text white, smooth transition
  - Description (DM Sans, #6B7280):
    "A single workspace where developers write, collaborate, 
    and build with AI — no tab switching, no merge conflicts, 
    no friction. Just code."
  - Bottom: "→ codesync.ai" link placeholder styled as subtle text link

Card entrance: scale from 0.95 + fade in on scroll

── 5. VISION SECTION ──
id="vision", padding 120px vertical

Full-width, centered, max-w-2xl:
- Section label: "OUR VISION"
- Large pull quote style (Syne 42px, weight 300, line-height 1.3, 
  center aligned):
  "Every important problem left to solve will eventually run on software. 
  We want to be the team that builds the tools the solvers use."
- Below: thin line + "— Devloom Technologies, 2024"
- Subtle background: single large blurred blue circle behind text, 
  opacity 0.04

Animate: text reveals word by word (Framer Motion, stagger 0.03s per word)

── 6. CONTACT / FOOTER ──
id="contact", bg #080B12, padding 80px vertical, 
border-top: 1px solid #1E2B42

Two columns:
Left:
  - DevloomLogo size="md"  
  - "Building something worth using." (#6B7280, mt-3)
  - Social row (icons only, placeholder hrefs="#"):
    GitHub icon, LinkedIn icon, Twitter/X icon
    Each: #3E4E6A, hover → #3B82F6, transition smooth

Right (or centered on mobile):
  - "Get in touch" label
  - Email displayed as styled text (not a form):
    "hello@devloom.tech" — #3B82F6, hover underline
  - "We're early. We're building. We'd love to hear from you." 
    (#6B7280, small)

Bottom bar: 
"© 2024 Devloom Technologies. All rights reserved." centered, 
#3E4E6A, font-size 12px, border-top #1E2B42 mt-8 pt-6

=== ANIMATIONS SUMMARY ===
- Hero: staggered entrance (badge → h1 → sub → buttons), 
  each element fades up (y: 30 → 0, opacity 0 → 1)
- All sections: whileInView trigger, once: true, viewport: 20% threshold
- Navbar: framer motion presence for mobile menu
- Stat cards: stagger 0.1s each on scroll enter
- Product card: scale + fade
- Vision quote: word-by-word reveal
- Hover states: all interactive elements have smooth 200ms transitions
- Scroll progress bar: thin #3B82F6 line at very top of page 
  (useScroll + useSpring from framer-motion, scaleX the bar)

=== GLOBAL RULES ===
- Mobile responsive — all sections stack properly on <768px
- No placeholder images — use pure CSS shapes, gradients, or SVG only
- All text is real copy (provided above) — no lorem ipsum anywhere
- Smooth scroll behavior: html { scroll-behavior: smooth }
- Page title: "Devloom Technologies — Where ideas become infrastructure"
- Favicon: use a simple blue circle in index.html (inline SVG favicon)
- Write ALL files completely: 
    src/App.jsx
    src/components/Navbar.jsx
    src/components/Hero.jsx
    src/components/About.jsx
    src/components/Product.jsx
    src/components/Vision.jsx
    src/components/Footer.jsx
    src/components/DevloomLogo.jsx
    src/index.css (global styles, dot grid, font imports)
    index.html (title + favicon)
    tailwind.config.js (extend with brand colors + Syne font)

After all files, give:
1. Exact install commands
2. Dev server start command
3. Test checklist:
   a. Hero loads with staggered animation
   b. Navbar blur works on scroll
   c. All section animations trigger on scroll
   d. Mobile menu works
   e. Smooth scroll to sections on nav click